    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Rare find alert! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 we're talking a flawless, like-new interior with zero visible wear, a stunning exterior free of scratches, dents, or blemishes, and a mechanically perfect powertrain that runs and drives as smooth as the day it left the factory. Everything works exactly as it should, and the attention to care this vehicle has received is evident the moment you lay eyes on it. If you've been searching for a truly turn-key, top-tier vehicle you can be proud of, this is the one!",
